title: Vestal remains unbeaten and unscored upon
text: Wednesday, October 07, 2015 - 10:02:25 PM Local Sports Vestal remains unbeaten and unscored upon 10/6/2015 (Updated 10:51:49 PM) The Vestal Golden Bears improve to 10-0 on the season with a 3-0 win over Ithaca, with no goals scored against them this season. The Bears are ranked third in the state in Class A after the latest rankings were released Tuesday. The U-E Tigers fall to the Horseheads 3-1.
